column5: This Vent-Hole (hereinafter known as IVH) if lost or stolen will not be replaced or purchase price refunded. Violation of IVH rules will result in expulsion without refund. A copy of IVH rules can be obtained from one or more members wearing tie-dyed Oxford shirts after written requests. Frivolity and silliness are highly recommended for all riders. Flamewars are expressly forbidden. Please consult your counselor magistrate or religious functionary before usage. Comment below if you agree. Tonight's lineup: Jimmy Kimmel: Riz Ahmed Andra DayJimmy Fallon: Michael Strahan Tig Notaro Emmy BlotnickStephen Colbert: Anthony Hopkins Florian Zeller Sen. Mazie HironoSeth Meyers: Catherine Zeta-Jones Wyatt Russell Emmanuelle CapletteJames Corden: Ron Funches Karol G How was your weekend?  I'm still not feeling very frivolous but I have been enjoying the wildflowers everywhere I go around the bay.     Meanwhile... in case there was any doubt.
